Added Split-By option to use Y as the column to split the load uniformly to all the mappers.Assuming the minimum value of Y is 0 and Maximum value is 1000. 

--username 
root 
--password 
password 
--connect 
jdbc:mysql://host_name:port/table_name 
--fields-terminated-by 
'|' 
--target-dir 
/user/arshaq/sqoop_challenge 
--split-by 
Y
-m
5 
--table
X
--target-dir
/user/arshaq/sqoop

